{"tid":1538444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"完啦好嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:18.000Z","uid":312053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1872b72e7fceee29f0dd96e1c4e27054633b8cb0","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"熊先生 (25歲) - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁先生 (35歲) - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧小姐 (21歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu (29歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐 (28歲) - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生 (32歲) - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生 (26歲) - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生 (25歲) - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生 (16歲) - 2/9/2019<br />\n<br />\n只要你記得佢地 就知單單撒回唔係一個終結<br />\n唔好再用文字藝術呃鳩我地<br />\n就算撒回 只會係4大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5EUjhp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5EUjhp.jpg&h=9353d705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n善忘嘅香港人 <br />\n仲記唔記得當初見到呢張圖嘅感覺<br />\n只要你仲有感覺 <br />\n單係撒回 你都應該繼續堅持！"},{"pid":"6b819c0407c08740435172d2ea70c3db5bec9a97","tid":1538444,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fb09f928e4da04e446e26e465ddcb44f6c48e6","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:36.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"4a5c79574574e439fb680d4091445c5e36b4db01","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"3c22981fe4962a924fce332a2cc45c5015cf428b","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"ddff3b5fa0d13bccf442fc610f97a7d050debd98","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:12.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"158fde15fedf699768788250c1ef848139f58d29","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"1c67f8ccbe9689b08d391d731845bd1d338e39a4","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"c3c00ade57c7fff03935940b9af1e750e1697199","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:48.000Z","msg":"自推7/10"},{"pid":"c7fe8678d6fb799f128f126d03f794dca5d27abe","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"自推8/10"},{"pid":"29676ebdb1dd9d9933625e289d89e9495b8c89a6","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"自推9/10"},{"pid":"084dafa791bb662f47a0dd684788703de47bc856","tid":1538444,"uid":312053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"自推10/10"}]}